    <item>
      <title>Hugo configuration</title>
      <link>https://tmichoel.github.io/simple-examples/hugo-configuration/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Oct 2021 21:04:50 +0200</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://tmichoel.github.io/simple-examples/hugo-configuration/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;hugo&#34;&gt;Hugo&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This site is written in &lt;a href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/&#34;&gt;Hugo&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;mathjax&#34;&gt;MathJax&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I used &lt;a href=&#34;https://geoffruddock.com/math-typesetting-in-hugo/&#34;&gt;this approach&lt;/a&gt; to enable &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.mathjax.org/&#34;&gt;MathJax&lt;/a&gt;, with the minor edit that step 2 needed to be applied to the file &amp;ldquo;head.html&amp;rdquo; instead of &amp;ldquo;header.html&amp;rdquo; (this seems to be specific to the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/LukasJoswiak/etch&#34;&gt;etch theme&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Inline math &lt;code&gt;$E=mc^2$&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Display math:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$f(x)=\int_0^x \sqrt{x-y} \sin(y) dy$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$p\wedge q \to r$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;github&#34;&gt;Github&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To set things up on Github, I followed &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.mytechramblings.com/posts/create-a-website-with-hugo-and-gh/&#34;&gt;these instructions&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;images&#34;&gt;Images&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;comments-and-discussion&#34;&gt;Comments and discussion&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mostly I followed this &lt;a href=&#34;https://zhauniarovich.com/post/2021/2021-06-giscus/&#34;&gt;tutorial&lt;/a&gt; to set up &lt;a href=&#34;https://giscus.app&#34;&gt;giscus&lt;/a&gt;, upto the configuration of giscus parameters in the hugo configuration file. There instead I set the following in the &lt;code&gt;[params]&lt;/code&gt; section (replace &lt;code&gt;&amp;quot;repo_id&amp;quot;&lt;/code&gt; etc. by the correct values):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-json&#34; data-lang=&#34;json&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;params&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;#&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;Other&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;parameters&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;#&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;Giscus&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;paramaters&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;giscus_commentable&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;page&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;true,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;post&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;giscus_repo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;repo_name&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;giscus_repo_id&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;repo_id&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;giscus_category&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Announcements&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;giscus_category_id&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;category_id&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;giscus_mapping&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;pathname&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;giscus_label&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;comment&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;giscus_theme&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;preferred_color_scheme&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;giscus_reactions_enabled&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;These parameters are read by a &lt;code&gt;giscus.html&lt;/code&gt; file stored in the &lt;code&gt;layouts/partials/&lt;/code&gt; of the theme containing:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-html&#34; data-lang=&#34;html&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;script&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;src&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;https://giscus.app/client.js&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;        &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;data-repo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;{{site.Params.giscus_repo}}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;        &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;data-repo-id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;{{site.Params.giscus_repo_id}}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;        &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;data-category&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;{{site.Params.giscus_category}}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;        &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;data-category-id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;{{site.Params.giscus_category_id}}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;        &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;data-mapping&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;{{site.Params.giscus_mapping}}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;        &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;data-reactions-enabled&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;{{site.Params.giscus_reactions_enabled}}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;        &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;data-theme&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;{{site.Params.giscus_theme}}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;        &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;crossorigin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;anonymous&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;        &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;async&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;script&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;noscript&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;Please enable JavaScript to view the comments powered by giscus.&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;noscript&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Finally I added the following line at the bottom of the file &lt;code&gt;layouts/partials/footer.html&lt;/code&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-json&#34; data-lang=&#34;json&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;.Params.giscus&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;partial&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;giscus.html&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Now if you set &lt;code&gt;giscus: true&lt;/code&gt; in the header of a post (similar to the MathJax solution above), comments should appear on that post.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
